A majestic, swirling vortex of blue and purple energy erupts from a serene, ancient jungle clearing, illuminating a towering, intricately carved stone statue of a humanoid figure - Bora Pra Xinxa - radiating power, with multiple miniature, newly summoned creatures (wolves, raptors, and smaller elemental-like beings) emerging from the vortex around him, detailed fantasy art, epic scale, dramatic lighting, Magic The Gathering style.